 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# CogVideoX-5B I2V on Kaggle (T4 x1 优化版)\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Kaggle 免费 T4 16GB 上跑 CogVideoX 图生视频，用极端内存优化。\n",
    "\n",
    "## ⚡ 使用前准备\n",
    "\n",
    "**1. 打开 GPU**\n",
    "- 右侧 **Settings** → **Accelerator** → 选 **GPU T4 x1**（免费版最高）\n",
    "- **Internet** → **On**\n",
    "\n",
    "**2. 上传模板图**\n",
    "- **+ Add Data** → 上传你的模板图（如 `character_template.png`）\n",
    "- 记下路径，填到 Cell 3 的 `IMAGE_PATH`\n",
    "\n",
    "**3. 如果 OOM**\n",
    "- 降低 WIDTH/HEIGHT（如 256x384）或 NUM_FRAMES（如 8）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 装依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!pip install -q diffusers transformers accelerate torchvision opencv-python pillow"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 检查 GPU"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!nvidia-smi"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 设置参数"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# ==== ✏️ 修改这些 ====\n",
    "IMAGE_PATH = \"/kaggle/input/你的数据集名/character_template.png\"  # ← 改成你的路径\n",
    "OUTPUT_DIR = \"/kaggle/working/\"\n",
    "PROMPT = \"a cute anime mother holding her baby, gentle horizontal sway, warm pastel colors, simple background\"\n",
    "NEGATIVE_PROMPT = \"ugly, blurry, deformed, text, watermark, complex background, realistic\"\n",
    "SEED = 42\n",
    "\n",
    "# 16GB T4 安全参数（如果 OOM 继续降低）\n",
    "NUM_FRAMES = 8           # 帧数，T4 x1 建议 8-12\n",
    "NUM_STEPS = 20           # 推理步数\n",
    "GUIDANCE_SCALE = 6.0\n",
    "WIDTH = 320              # 宽度，T4 x1 建议 256-384\n",
    "HEIGHT = 512             # 高度，保持 9:16 比例\n",
    "# =====================\n",
    "\n",
    "import os\n",
    "os.makedirs(OUTPUT_DIR, exist_ok=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 加载模型（带内存优化）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "from diffusers import CogVideoXImageToVideoPipeline\n",
    "from diffusers.utils import export_to_video\n",
    "from PIL import Image\n",
    "import time\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Loading model (first run downloads ~2GB)...\")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "\n",
    "pipe = CogVideoXImageToVideoPipeline.from_pretrained(\n",
    "    \"THUDM/CogVideoX-5b-I2V\",\n",
    "    torch_dtype=torch.bfloat16\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# === 内存优化三件套 ===\n",
# === 内存优化 ===
pipe.enable_sequential_cpu_offload()   # 逐层卸载，最省显存
pipe.enable_attention_slicing()        # 分片注意力计算
pipe.vae.enable_tiling()               # VAE 分块处理
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Done in {time.time()-t0:.1f}s\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. 跑推理"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print(f\"Loading image: {IMAGE_PATH}\")\n",
    "image = Image.open(IMAGE_PATH).convert(\"RGB\")\n",
    "print(f\"Original size: {image.size}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "image = image.resize((WIDTH, HEIGHT), Image.LANCZOS)\n",
    "print(f\"Resized to: {image.size}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nGenerating {NUM_FRAMES} frames @ {WIDTH}x{HEIGHT}...\")\n",
    "t0 = time.time()\n",
    "\n",
    "generator = torch.Generator(device=\"cpu\").manual_seed(SEED)\n",
    "\n",
    "with torch.inference_mode():\n",
    "    video_frames = pipe(\n",
    "        prompt=PROMPT,\n",
    "        image=image,\n",
    "        num_frames=NUM_FRAMES,\n",
    "        guidance_scale=GUIDANCE_SCALE,\n",
    "        num_inference_steps=NUM_STEPS,\n",
    "        generator=generator,\n",
    "        negative_prompt=NEGATIVE_PROMPT,\n",
    "    ).frames[0]\n",
    "\n",
    "elapsed = time.time() - t0\n",
    "print(f\"Done in {elapsed:.1f}s ({len(video_frames)} frames, {elapsed/len(video_frames):.1f}s/frame)\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 保存 + 预览"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "output_file = os.path.join(OUTPUT_DIR, \"cogvideo_output.mp4\")\n",
    "export_to_video(video_frames, output_file, fps=4)  # 帧数少时用低 fps\n",
    "print(f\"Saved: {output_file}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Size: {os.path.getsize(output_file)/1024/1024:.1f} MB\")\n",
    "\n",
    "from IPython.display import Video, display\n",
    "display(Video(output_file, width=480))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 显存监测（可选）"
   ]
  },
  {
